      "role": "user",
      "content": "I'm not sure I follow what you mean by \"goblins\" here. Can you give me a serious technical breakdown of the logs? Specifically, why would the worker process terminate abruptly like that if it's just a connection pool issue? Is there a specific resource exhaustion or a deadlock scenario you're seeing in the logs?",
